- Where are what?

264
00:14:11.716 --> 00:14:13.978
My PTA notes
for the meeting tonight!

265
00:14:13.979 --> 00:14:15.284
They were right here
on the counter.

266
00:14:15.285 --> 00:14:16.459
and now they're not here.

267
00:14:16.460 --> 00:14:17.721
