357
00:20:01.805 --> 00:20:02.850
Oh. we insist.

358
00:20:03.938 --> 00:20:05.243
Don't we. Cece?

359
00:20:07.594 --> 00:20:08.595
Um...

360
00:20:09.944 --> 00:20:11.467
I hope you guys like it.

361
00:20:34.142 --> 00:20:35.317
Come in.

362
00:20:37.798 --> 00:20:39.842
Hey.

363
00:20:39.843 --> 00:20:41.758
