left on your sentence.

441
00:24:35.949 --> 00:24:38.254
And I don't like that for you.

442
00:24:38.255 --> 00:24:40.170
I don't like that
for me. either.

443
00:24:49.266 --> 00:24:51.050
- Hi. Nina. I'm just...
- I need you to pick up Cece

444
00:24:51.051 --> 00:24:53.966
